## What you get

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Body** | Scaled sphere with a lighter belly underneath |
| **Tail** | Curved `ShapeGeometry` on a pivot that wags ~6 Hz |
| **Fins** | Dorsal + two pectoral fins from curved shapes |
| **Eyes** | White + pupil + highlight spheres |
| **Scales** | 60 tiny dots scattered on the upper/back surface |
| **Mouth** | Half-torus ring |
| **Animation** | Fish swims a gentle figure-8, tail wags, dorsal ripples |
| **Environment** | Rising translucent bubbles, swaying seaweed, sandy floor, fog |
| **Interaction** | `OrbitControls` – drag to orbit, scroll to zoom |

